The task is to create a box object, make it blue and center it on the screen both vertically and horizontally
Here is how to do it:
=============================================================================================================

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <style>
        body {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh; /* Makes the body fill the viewport height */
            margin: 0; /* Removes default margin */
        }
        .box {
            height: 100px;
            width: 100px;
            background-color: lightblue; /* Added for visibility */
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="box"></div>
</body>
</html>
